# Mom's Kitchen - Food Ordering App

Mom's Kitchen is a user-friendly food ordering platform designed to bring convenience and joy to food enthusiasts everywhere.

## Key Features

- Browse delicious food items organized by various categories üçïü•ó
- Easily add and remove items to/from your favorites ‚ù§Ô∏è
- Conveniently manage your cart for seamless ordering üõí
- Explore your past order history for quick reordering üìú
- Enjoy an intuitive user interface with smooth navigation for a delightful experience üì±üí®

## Technologies Used

- Firebase Authentication: Secure user sign-up, login, and password management üîê
- Firebase Realtime Database: Instantly show menu items and user information üîÑ
- Lottie Animation: Enhance user experience with captivating animations üéâ
- Picasso Image Loading: Load and display images seamlessly from the database üñºÔ∏è
- Google Location Services: Utilize location permissions for streamlined address details üó∫Ô∏è



## Frontend Files (Java)

### Activities
- `MainActivity.java`: Main activity showing food items.
- `AddLocationDetailsActivity.java`: Activity for adding location details.
- `ForgotPasswordActivity.java`: Activity for resetting password.
- `HomeActivity.java`: Home activity.
- `OrderHistoryDetailsActivity.java`: Activity for displaying order history details.
- `OrderPageActivity.java`: Activity for displaying order page.
- `PaymentMethodActivity.java`: Activity for selecting payment method.
- `SignUpActivity.java`: Activity for user sign-up.
- `SplashScreenActivity.java`: Splash screen activity.

### Fragments
- `FavouritesFragment.java`: Fragment for managing favorite food items.
- `MenuFragment.java`: Fragment for displaying menu items.
- `OrderHistoryFragment.java`: Fragment for displaying order history.
- `ProfileFragment.java`: Fragment for managing user profile.

### Adapters
- `AddressBoxAdapter.java`: Adapter for address box.
- `FavouritesBoxAdapter.java`: Adapter for favorites box.
- `FoodBoxAdapter.java`: Adapter for food box.
- `OrderBoxAdapter.java`: Adapter for order box.
- `OrderHistoryCartAdapter.java`: Adapter for order history cart.
- `OrderHistoryDisplayAdapter.java`: Adapter for order history display.

### Data Models
- `AddressData.java`: Data model for address.
- `FavouritesData.java`: Data model for favorites.
- `FoodBoxData.java`: Data model for food box.
- `OrderData.java`: Data model for order.
- `OrderHistoryCartData.java`: Data model for order history cart.
- `OrderHistoryDisplayData.java`: Data model for order history display.
- `Users.java`: Data model for users.

## Backend Files (XML)

### Layouts
- `activity_add_location_details.xml`: Layout for adding location details.
- `activity_forgot_password.xml`: Layout for resetting password.
- `activity_main.xml`: Layout for the main activity.
- `activity_menu.xml`: Layout for displaying menu items.
- `activity_order_history_details.xml`: Layout for displaying order history details.
- `activity_order_page.xml`: Layout for displaying order page.
- `activity_payment_method.xml`: Layout for selecting payment method.
- `activity_select_location.xml`: Layout for selecting location.
- `activity_sign_up.xml`: Layout for user sign-up.
- `activity_splash_screen.xml`: Layout for the splash screen.
- `address_box.xml`: Layout for address box.
- `confirmation_box.xml`: Layout for confirmation box.
- `error_box.xml`: Layout for error box.
- `favourites_box.xml`: Layout for favorites box.
- `food_box.xml`: Layout for food box.
- `fragment_favourites.xml`: Layout for favorites fragment.
- `fragment_home.xml`: Layout for home fragment.
- `fragment_order_history.xml`: Layout for order history fragment.
- `fragment_profile.xml`: Layout for profile fragment.
- `order_box.xml`: Layout for order box.
- `order_history_cart_box.xml`: Layout for order history cart box.
- `order_history_display_box.xml`: Layout for order history display box.
- `permission_box.xml`: Layout for permission box.
- `quantity_box.xml`: Layout for quantity box.

